To build the container, cd into the prometheus-firehose directory and call

> docker build -t prometheus-firehose:latest .

Add this to your config

prometheus:
  enabled: true
  process_filter:
    - include:
        port: 5005

and run

> docker run -d -p 5005:5005 prometheus-firehose


OR alternatively add just this to your config

prometheus:
  enabled: true

and run

> docker run -d -p 5005:5005 -l io.prometheus.scrape=true -l io.prometheus.port=5005 prometheus-firehose
